BGP Encodings and Procedures for
Multicast in MPLS/BGP IP VPNs
2012", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC6514.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document describes the BGP encodings and procedures for exchanging the information elements required by Multicast in MPLS/BGP IP VPNs, as specified in RFC 6513. [STANDARDS-TRACK]"];
